<!-- 1.2.23 -->
<div class="toload proposition">
<p><span class="envidentifier">Proposition 1.2.23</span>
An element $p$ of an inverse semigroup $S$ is a zero (minimum) of $S$ if and only if it is absorbing (that is, $ps=p$ for all $s\in S$).
</p>
</div>